Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.64,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(145,700)\fad(1029,0)}第十五话\N残心难解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这树被称为神木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.00,Text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(1124,995)}九久能木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有助于伤痛的恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:57.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且神木还能免除无明之灾厄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:58.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在还要好好静卧休息才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,发不出声音来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像笹目 但是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 比起身体所受的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,心里的伤痕更深更痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:44.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己主动要求成为界联系统的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:01.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司也不愿意被人丢下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个戴在身上暂时就不会有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了 这女人不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和骸在一起来着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人的话直接就回晌在我的脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:41.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但却听不到我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你的声音我听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,猜对了？你是在想这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是感觉到你在想事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却感受不到你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心在惊恐战栗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为恐惧而紧紧地封闭了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才感受不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你肯对我敞开心扉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少开口说话应该还是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:36.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心在惊恐战栗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这边呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他会不会有事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他的命一直都很硬的 应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,相信啊…说说总是很轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:26.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间时而思维会联结在一起不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样总觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,反而语言却越发可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:38.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可心里却完全不这样认为什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我连跟你都要说谎这是要闹哪样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有些话就不要说出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:47.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:03.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心意不就瞒不下去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那伊削平人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:12.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,全身大约40％尸钢化了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,40%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这不是很少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:23.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 很难想象他在无明领域中心那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:28.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是和艾米露的持续共信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,及平人强烈的自我意识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,形成了保护屏障吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,里面暗无天日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都和艾米露联结着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但赤司他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:04.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果因为笹目的关系内心产生动摇的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话我们能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有什么我们现在能做的就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我当时应该拦下的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托帮我盯一下呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这 须酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:24.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不要在作战中散播负面情绪拖后腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你拦下？拦下谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司也好笹目也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是思考过 纠结过才下定的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你又凭什么去阻拦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司那时不也是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:54.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他说要一个人去无明领域的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:10:00.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时他的眼神和青司是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我肯定是拦不住他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 那个才是我们现在共同的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:15.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过去的事你再怎么后悔那东西也不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不以我们的意志为转移地步步紧逼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:20.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看还是有一些没有被尸钢化的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是有神木生长的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是在神木附近的话就没什么好担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个手环也是用神木枝编成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,会保护赤司的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,会保护赤司的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我本是想保护笹目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你却是在被她保护啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…会去打倒骸的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以等我回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果继续苦等的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,她会连成为界联系统的机会都错过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,最终抱恨死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:24.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们合为一体来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是为了你啊 赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我几时这样求过你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我本是想要保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想要救你这才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:55.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:05.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好傻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,住手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,住手呀 不要伤害赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:41.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会伤害你 我不是你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地被保妒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 你就由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:59.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又在被保护了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…再…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:32.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要再被保护了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于听到你的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我能说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你对我敞开心扉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,出了好多血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹…目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:23.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是赤司也尸钢化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,界联系统的材料就要多到铺出来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,时至今日就算去找新的机师这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,托这帮蠢蛋的福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,损失掉那么多样本还真是心痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:50.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就不去动它了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:51.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:05.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有神木在生长所以没有完全尸钢化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这边呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我一起骑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:31.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:34.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的赤红
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为保护我而留下的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…保护了笹目？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我也保护了别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我保护了笹目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像记得以前有过这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这无明领域里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在一起避雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:14.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时你被雨淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}这样会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我把外衣披给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要你的外衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,别走呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:00.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我·的·名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去避雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:28.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,骸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是骸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:44.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有死哦 只是在小歇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像很累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:47.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,它说它好痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来跟它道个歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 你看它在颤抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜啊 被你吓得在颤抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:07.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不都是你的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 都是因为它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你才成了界联系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,成了界联系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你没有成为界联系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还好好的就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:37.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 今天开始赤司也一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人一直在一起~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:45.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:54.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会和我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:20:00.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一直…永远都在一起 赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:04.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我可以不用再寻找了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:09.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时明明找得那么辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:09.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}去哪了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}赤…赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:30.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在寻找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:37.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可不许这张嘴再叫那个名字了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:46.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于想起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底都做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是保护了笹目…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,她还说要一直在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:10.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对 笹目她…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那机体里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你救了赤司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:22.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:26.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见啊 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:33.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You lose your mind, you crash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A nervous breakdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You feel an urge inside, you crush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no escape now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You try to change your life, you jump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Another letdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But then you hear a voice inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You gotta open up your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See the life bestowed on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blinded by reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Broken ideology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heart in captivity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Exceeding the borders within
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seize your capability
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Endless possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Find your individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take pride, let the chase begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me what direction you think I should take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I know I'm gonna find the way』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me that this sable is for my own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『Hear what I've got to say』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me to believe the decisions you make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I'm facing a new day』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So open up your blinded eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop living a lie and start living your life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today you're falling away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today I'm breaking away
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,失汝心志　躯形难继
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,慌乱分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心潮涌动　冲荡破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,已是无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,逆天改命　奋力跃腾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,再落心灰意冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却闻心中轻语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,放眼茫然四顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,但见尘世夺予
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,现实毁盲双目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,仅余碎裂思悟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心亦牢牢禁锢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,勿言轻弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,跨越心中束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,紧握汝力天成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,迸发无尽可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,寻汝真我个性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,昂首迈步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫要擅自定吾前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾定将自寻通途』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫言黑暗皆为吾敌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『但得静闻吾倾诉』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫诳吾从尔等好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾自面崭新朝暮』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,故舍犹豫再开盲眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,挣脱谎言自立世间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,此时汝却飘然离去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,今日吾将突破禁锢
